             <lg> 
              <l>Fog over the base: the beams ranging</l>
          <l>From the five towers pull home from the night</l> 
          <l>The crews cold in fur, the bombers banging</l>
          <l>Kike lost trucks down the levels of the ice.</l>
          <l>A glow drifts in lke mist (how many tons of it?),</l>
          <l>Bounces to a roll, turns suddenly to steel</l>
          <l>And tires and turrets, huge in the trembling light</l>
          <l>The next is high, and pulls up with a wail,</l>
          <l>Comes round again-no use. And no use for the rest</l>
          
                 
